Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.44,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}本字幕由喵萌奶茶屋制作  仅供交流试看之用  请勿用于商业用途 \N\N翻译: Oscuro　校对: Dysonsphere　繁化: 雲棋　后期: MIR
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,跑步好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没见到老爷爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,机器狗也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希望人没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那个大爷已经坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,坏掉了也能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会神采奕奕地回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有庆典呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,已经发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,吗啡戒断反应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要给他吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一旦让他吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前开着卡车乱闯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为过量摄入吗啡所致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有两人被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还留他一命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在那孩子的生日庆典之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再出什么乱子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和我回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个可怜的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了孙女的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大地没受伤真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要隆重庆祝他的十岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您的高额捐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我能优先享受仪式了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这要视天启而定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你也只能这样回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我们也会金继的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说这是一处新裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,下面带您参观藏书阁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你很难受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,又是眨眼和手指敲击的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,摩尔斯电码 我随便打的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,摩尔斯电码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在打摩尔斯电码吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的话眨眼一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的话眨眼两次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是偶然眨了眨眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等 我看不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂摩尔斯电码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你能再来一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,最好一个字一个字地来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,オ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还是オ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,キ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ナ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ジ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,シ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ク
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ル
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,コ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,コ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,キ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,ケ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,即将有大型地震到来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,泰坦尼克号 SOS 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是渔夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是的小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,与收容地的交涉正在推进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,随机抽取的第一批人员开始转移
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有大地震要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以前也没出过事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我去跟妈妈说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个卧病在床的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是潜水艇的小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前不知道他为什么老眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是摩尔斯电码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他说有大地震要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们赶紧逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这让人怎么能不慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你刚刚说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,步 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是小野寺先生的情报是否正确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还需要进一步确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,切肉的菜刀是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是犯了什么事被抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请救救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大地震要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这么吓人的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别毁了我们的庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,地震根本预测不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是很安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是来自小野寺的准确情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小野寺又是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把他给老子带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是潜水艇驾驶员小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那个说日本要沉没的小野寺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那他人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里的疗养大楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也很危险 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是大麻起火烧过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在这么重要的日子里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个老不死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的太疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我吗啡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你这要完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,难道巨像也要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要这样 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大谷叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,出丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我把菜刀拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,刚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然只是块头大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但也能派上用场对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,刚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个打假赛被除名的关取力士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经无处可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,刚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请您抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请带大家离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要舍弃这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都他妈在搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,给老子开门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把门撞开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你别挤我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这些归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会交给你啊 真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真敢打我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 是你打开金库的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都不把我放在眼里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们又来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看来大家目的相同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一楼已经出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,走楼上出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子还在上面等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人没找到 但是钥匙在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,叶惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,救救大地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.98,Top,,0,0,0,,谢 谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你孙女？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子不是你的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孙女被泥石流冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望她在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听听孙女的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以听到我孙女的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你孙女让我这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,烟也别抽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,说了不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快 上车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔也快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是普通的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听到那个人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一直守望着你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再会了 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么跟刚交代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己去说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给你 当是饯别了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷爷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快开车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,安全驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爷 爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个母亲当得真失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里他才能活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的最后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,或许就是希望你不要召唤他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请你为了自己活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉他这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不能止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我们和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我这条命都是你给的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我和你们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要糟蹋自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你创造了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都被需要的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和大家一起迈向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是哪里出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的能力要为了这孩子而使用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世上没有无用的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,创造一个这孩子也能获得尊严的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一张了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,火山活动已经稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:23:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,日本不会立即沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家冷静对待 不要做出过激行为
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不论去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那里也绝不会是黄泉
